                            <comment id="14056136" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Wed, 9 Jul 2014 11:41:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A manual workaround would be to use the oak-console and delete the &apos;async&apos; property under the root path in the &apos;:async&apos; node: _/:async &lt;/p&gt;
